 {
  "text": "Hi, Paula. This is David. Welcome to your first week. Let me tell you about my day here. I start at eight o'clock. I have a coffee, and I read my emails. At nine, I talk to my team. I usually meet two or three clients every day. I travel on Tuesdays — I visit brokers in Rio. I don't work on weekends. Never. Your first meeting is on Monday, at ten. See you there. Goodbye.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_listening_david.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Good morning, Paula. Sofia here. You ask me about my week — so, here it is. I start at nine, and I finish at six. Every morning I talk to my team for ten minutes. Ten minutes, no more. I meet clients on Wednesdays and Thursdays. I travel once a month — I visit our office in Lima. And I don't answer emails after seven. That is my rule. Your routine is your rule too. Welcome, Paula.",
